metadata.name: alexXxa
metadata.description:
I had a dream about a green girl that was half spider, so I drew a green girl that is half spider. 

This was a fun piece to make because I was able to explore a new realm of art that I haven't tried before. Pixelated animation is definitely a fun new venture for me and I can't wait to see the impact it has on my creativity. 

Thanks for lending me your eyes for a moment, lol.
